{"tid":452830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放眼五年：香港未來    學者：淪陷不可避免","createTime":"2017-10-30T14:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T16:04:43.000Z","uid":20058,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"08b7ae590fef7c765d52b5b49ceab8e148b29dca","tid":452830,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T14:54:20.000Z","msg":"習近平說要對香港落實全面管治權，學者認為，現在內地高層有一種想法，就是香港已不如過往般重要，因為內地已經「發展得很強大了」。他認為香港在過去20年已變了樣，所以未來的淪陷，不可避免。<br />\n<br />\n他們亦認為，香港已由過往展示一國兩制的櫥窗，變成了民族統一的美好樣板，所以未來只會有更多人，出來說要繁榮穩定，不容街頭出現搗亂情況。<br />\n<br />\n#放眼五年<br />\n#香港未來<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1541444922666655/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1541444922666655%2F&d=S6cB4ciL2boPXDS%2BKOaE2dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b800d9c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1541444922666655/</a>"},{"pid":"e98dd8faa3e88b0908c05058e07b019ab61bb28f","tid":452830,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T14:57:09.000Z","msg":"BNO平權"},{"pid":"cc1c1596317a15716545b97cccab93bb01a030e8","tid":452830,"uid":141574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T14:59:46.000Z","msg":"未來先淪陷？"},{"pid":"b8ba6d9b74e2c2dcb67484bc4a01841cf4fefe2f","tid":452830,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T15:00:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>屌你老母五毛狗急跳牆冒認會員擾亂視聽妖言惑眾使唔使BAM<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/223419_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt